name: Mors 'Lamafa & Saguni'
description:
L.-../A.-/M--/A.-/F..-./A.-
S.../A.-/G--./U..-/N-./I.. 
-
-
Melompat, menikam lewat jari tergenggam
Lamafa tangguh bertenaga penuh
Perahu terangkat, dan terbalik, dan terhantam
Sisa satu, 7 tenggelam.

Matahari mengambang di permukaan, 
melerai Lamafa dan Saguni yg berhadapan
di kedalaman Lamalera.

*****
Lamafa (Juru Tikam Paus)
Saguni (Paus Pembunuh)

____________________________

The tough Lamafa was full force
Leapt, stabbed, with fingers held
The boat was hit, and lifted, and flipped
One Lamafa remaining, 7 drowned.

The sunset floats on the surface, 
interfering Lamafa and Saguni 
who face each other in the depth of Lamalera.

*****
Lamafa (Whale Hunter)
Saguni (Killer Whale)

----

I hope that is correct translation,
inspired from my old prose (Nov 2013, Tumblr era)

This is my token of gratitude.
